creator: Marek Dobrowolski
descriptionHtml:
Build your own cartoon world! You don't need to know how to draw or paint to free your creativity.

• Arrange, rotate and combine building blocks.
• Use bricks, stone or wood to build a house or a medieval castle.
• Construct sailing ships, space vehicles or robots.
• Draw comic scenes with pirates, dinosaurs, ancient warriors and more.
• Add decorations, cartoon characters, background landscapes and comic book effects.
• Share your creations as PNG images.
title: Toon Blocks: Build Anything
